reviews.text: The food is ok. The service is very good.

Just a alright Korean BBQ place. Not much food and drinks choices and its a bit cramped. Not like other Korean BBQ restaurant, all alcohol drinks are NOT free. With that price tag, might not consider eating here again.
HK ver. on Korean BBQ.
Decent AYCE Korean BBQ. You order each piece of meat individually, which actually allows you to control your pace a bit more. Overall, the meats were average. The fried chicken is really good!
Very good food. Leave before 7:20pm and u will get a 30% off discount. A great value of money.

reviews.text: 食物不差，人未齊比我地等待，人齊才計鐘
食物還不錯，冷氣和抽風有點弱，枱也比較小，晚930後價錢很化算

呢間野  食品衛生唔講住  服務態度一般 預約是是但但
 野又唔好食 真係無下次
韓燒食品種類多，限時二小時用餐，價錢畧貴，食物出品水平一般，汽水及無酒精飲品免費。

食物種類有熟食及韓燒，都算多選擇，味道一般，未有特別出色。
服務質素未有太大感受到，只可以話可以同木無表情，見到待應傳送食物見，D水邊行邊漏到一地都係，仍然無反應，唔太細心。
樓下搭電梯排長龍上去都要等15mins!🤦🏻‍♀️🤦🏻‍♀️
